reviewText: Big fan of The Lone Ranger! I remember this series as a kid, I had to have this, for my collection! Great quality DVD, good price!

reviewText: As a huge lone ranger fan i was curious about some cartoon adventures so ipurchased this havent watched any yet but im sure i'll love and service was great arrived fast.
Title: New Adventures of the Lone Ranger

reviewText: Another animated gem. The Lone Ranger is another one of my all-tme favorite westerns, along with Zorro. This dvd is great and would like to get The New Adventures of The Lone Ranger and Zorro Vol.2 new, if price is reasonable,(different dvd from this one).
Title: New Adventures of the Lone Ranger

reviewText: Far better than the recent Verbinski version.  This cartoon gets the spirit of the Lone Ranger and treats his legend appropriately.  Not for all tastes, but pretty good for the young 'uns.
Title: New Adventures of the Lone Ranger

reviewText: i love cartoons know a days and kids today are missing out because this cartoon could stack up against todays cartoons.
Title: New Adventures of the Lone Ranger

reviewText: I used to watch this series on tv and I had to get it on dvd. It's a great series, A+++!
Title: New Adventures of the Lone Ranger

reviewText: The animation is what you would expect from this era, unfortunately. Very stiff, a LOT of recycled motions/actions. The plots are a little slow and convoluted, but my 3-year-old still loves it, so it did it's job.
Title: New Adventures of the Lone Ranger

reviewText: I fully admit to buying this because my version of a meltdown about getting older is not to buy a faster car and cheat on my wife. Nope. It's to snuggle up with my wife and force her to relieve MY "thrilling days of yester-year" by watching cartoons and movies that I adored as a kid. No matter how bad they are.
Title: New Adventures of the Lone Ranger

reviewText: Another great produced by Filmation studios back in early 80s. I especially remembered and loved the orchestral theme song. So dramatic. A great buy as you anxiously await the theatrical release of new Walt Disney film with Armie Hammer and Johnny Depp.
Title: New Adventures of the Lone Ranger
